OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FMore than 50 new emergency areas are
OL,7,Fto be installed on the M25 and
OL,8,Fsurrounding motorways in the South
OL,9,FEast as part of a nationwide safety
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,FThe move follows a widespread campaign
OL,13,Ffor safety improvements on smart
OL,14,Fmotorways after a number of deaths.
OL,15,FNational Highways says safety is its
OL,16,F"highest priority".
