OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FTwenty four new emergency areas are
OL,7,Fplanned for two sections of the M25,
OL,8,Fbetween junctions 23 and 27 in
OL,9,FHertfordshire and Essex, and between
OL,10,Fjunctions 5 and 7 in Surrey and Kent.
OL,12,FConstruction is due to begin in
OL,13,FHertfordshire and Essex from Thursday
OL,14,F25 April 2024.
OL,16,FThe M20 in Kent, M3 in Surrey and
OL,17,FHampshire and M4 in Berkshire will
OL,18,Falso see upgrades to install more
OL,19,Femergency areas from late April and
OL,20,Fearly May, with the M27 in Hampshire
OL,21,Ffollowing later in the summer.
