OL,6,FFifty two emergency areas are to be
OL,7,Fbuilt in this phase of the programme
OL,8,Fon the M25 and neighbouring motorways,
OL,9,Fas follows:
OL,11,FThe upgrades are part of work to add
OL,12,Fmore emergency areas to all lane
OL,13,Frunning motorways across the country.
OL,15,FNational Highways says it's committed
OL,16,Fto building more than 150 new
OL,17,Femergency areas to give drivers more
OL,18,Fplaces to stop in an emergency.
