OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FThirteen have already been installed
OL,7,Fand opened for traffic, eight on the
OL,8,FM1 in Bedfordshire and
OL,9,FNorthamptonshire and five on the M6 in
OL,10,FStaffordshire.
OL,12,FConstruction is already underway on 12
OL,13,Fmore emergency areas on the M1 in
OL,14,FSouth Yorkshire, 10 between junctions
OL,15,F30 and 31 on the M1 in Derbyshire, and
OL,16,F12 on the M6 between junctions 21A and
OL,17,F26 in Cheshire.
