OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FLast month, start of work on a further
OL,7,F54 emergency areas on the M1 and M5
OL,8,Fmotorways in the Midlands was
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FEmergency areas provide a place to
OL,12,Fstop for drivers in an emergency if
OL,13,Fthey are unable to leave the motorway
OL,14,For stop at a service area.
OL,16,FThey are signposted at regular
OL,17,Fintervals and have bright orange road
OL,18,Fsurfaces to help drivers identify them.
