OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FEach area is 100 metres long meaning
OL,7,Fthere is space for all types of
OL,8,Fvehicles.
OL,10,FThey are also equipped with emergency
OL,11,Ftelephones linking directly to
OL,12,FNational Highways' control rooms to
OL,13,Fget help on the way quickly.
OL,15,FNational Highways Project Sponsor
OL,16,FFelicity Clayton said: "Safety is our
OL,17,Fhighest priority and we have listened
OL,18,Fto drivers' concerns about having more
OL,19,Fplaces to stop in an emergency on
OL,20,Fmotorways which don't have a permanent
OL,21,Fhard shoulder.
