OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,F"This is part of the Government's #900
OL,7,Fmillion investment in further safety
OL,8,Fimprovements on existing smart
OL,9,Fmotorways, which includes adding an
OL,10,Fadditional 150 emergency areas across
OL,11,Fthe network and giving motorists clear
OL,12,Fadvice when using smart motorways to
OL,13,Fboost public confidence."
OL,15,FFor the upgrade to be carried out
OL,16,Fsafely, the left-hand lane will be
OL,17,Fclosed throughout construction. Lanes
OL,18,Ftwo, three and four will remain open
OL,19,Fwith a 50mph speed limit in place.
