OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FThe work is being carefully
OL,7,Fcoordinated with other major
OL,8,Fimprovements already underway on the
OL,9,FM25, including junction 28, where the
OL,10,Fmotorway meets the A12 at the Brook
OL,11,FStreet roundabout in Essex, at
OL,12,Fjunction 10 near Wisley in Surrey,
OL,13,Fwhich involves a series of weekend
OL,14,Fclosures on the M25 and the A3 around
OL,15,Fthe junction.
OL,17,FNational Highways says that teams are
OL,18,Fworking "tirelessly" to coordinate all
OL,19,Fthis work closely and keep disruption
OL,20,Fto an absolute minimum.
