OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,FA spokesman said; "Our motorways are
OL,7,Fsome of the safest in the world, but
OL,8,Fwe appreciate that more work is needed
OL,9,Fto help everyone feel confident when
OL,10,Fusing sections of smart motorway.
OL,12,F"Smart motorways were introduced to
OL,13,Fprovide extra capacity on some of our
OL,14,Fbusiest and most congested sections of
OL,15,Fmotorway. shows that, overall, in
OL,16,Fterms of serious or fatal casualties,
OL,17,Fsmart motorways are the safest roads
OL,18,Fwe have.
