OL,3,CMore emergency areas to be installed
OL,4,Con smart motorways to improve safety
OL,6,F"We are continuing to listen to what
OL,7,Fpeople tell us and take action to
OL,8,Fclose the gap between how drivers'
OL,9,Ffeel and what the safety statistics
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,F"There is work to do as every road
OL,13,Fdeath is a tragedy and every serious
OL,14,Finjury a life changed. Safety is our
OL,15,Fpriority and we will never cease to
OL,16,Fstrive for the safest road network in
OL,17,Fthe world."
